<P><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
<IFRAME FRAMEBORDER=1 ALIGN=CENTER width=100% HEIGHT=200 SCROLLING=YES SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/Forum1/HTML/000055.html">
<TABLE BORDER=0 cellpadding=4 border=0 cellspacing=0 WIDTH="95%"><TR ><TD COLSPAN=2><CENTER><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="#F0DCA0" FACE="Verdana, Arial">T O P I C  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; R E V I E W</font></CENTER></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">lar</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hi All,<P>Just letting you know that if replies have been somewhat low key lately, it's been because of a real marathon development session we just had. New screenshots, new feature lists and replies to your questions coming up in the next day.<P>Lar</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtexture.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Anastasia</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">All right, I´m preparing the X-ray section of my brain for the new feature list  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/wink.gif"><BR>BTW, "Back from the dead": Where´s Marian ? He hasn´t posted in quite some time. Is he still in Norway ?</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Tutamun</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hi lar,<P>the last few days I was wondering if you were sick or something worse  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/wink.gif"> A bit more and I would have asked where everyone is. At least rat was there all the time.  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/smile.gif"> We've missed you.  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/smile.gif"></FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtexture.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Arhu</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Marian was on holiday and won't be back until January 9th, which is in fact tomorrow.  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/smile.gif"><BR>(Don't try to guess why I know that - I'm omniscient, of course!  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/wink.gif">)<P>Tutamun: Well, Lynn was there too...<P><I>Meow...</I><BR>Arhu<BR></FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Tutamun</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Well I don't count women...  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/badsmile.gif"><P>No thats not true, sorry Lynn, totaly forgot you.  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/wink.gif"><P>I also need a Holiday, quite urgent  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/frown.gif"></FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtexture.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">lynn</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">It's ok, I am used to it  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/wink.gif"></FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Deadlock</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">By the way Lar, is Larian Studios a company in Vlaanderen? (Dan kan ik namenlijk ook af en toe gewoon Nederlands praten.)</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtexture.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Arhu</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">No, you can't.  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/wink.gif"><BR>Because here are creatures of many different cultures and countries, and some wouldn't understand a single word of what you said. Anyway welcome, Deadlock!  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P><I>Meow..</I><BR>Arhu</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">rat</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">That's right, you can't.  You should always use English, except if you specifically write something in the freakzone^h^h^h^h^h^h^h^h^h german forum.</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtexture.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Bronthion</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Freakzone??? <P>Have you ever looked in your mirror, rat?  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/badsmile.gif"><P><P>------------------<BR>Bronthion, der dunkle Halb-Elf<BR>Bronthion, the dark Half-Elf<P></FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Astaroth</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Arhu,<P>Are you Dutch? Because you understood what Deadlock said...<BR><p>[This message has been edited by Astaroth (edited 10-01-2000).]</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtexture.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Arhu</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">No, I'm not, Astaroth. I just guessed, you know.  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/wink.gif"><BR>Well, to say the truth - I don't understand that language, but I thought it could be something like "Dann kann ich naemlich auch auf <I>? ? ?</I> Niederlaendisch...<I>?</I>", in English something like: "Then I can namely also ... in Dutch" or so.<BR>You see - it's somewhat similar.  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/smile.gif"><BR>And, err... I didn't see Merlin. Or did I? However, I didn't see it a few days ago. Maybe you mean Lynn?<P>Rat, freakzone? Yeah!  <IMG SRC="http://www.larian.com/ubb/smile.gif"><BR>Freak, freaky freak... free fried fired freaky freshwater frogs freezing frequently...<P><I>Meow...</I><BR>Arhu</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Astaroth</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Arhu,<P>Well you're close. It means: "Because then I could speak Dutch once in a while." But you did pretty well. Sorry about that Merlin stuff, it was Lynn. Just got confused a little, but as you can see I've set things straight. <P>Bye for now...</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
</IFRAME>
